snippet.title: Space Station 14 trailer - PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Want to live your best life, in space? Space Station 14 is a space station simulator that will let you fulfill one of a stack of different jobs to keep a space station running. Whether you want to be an engineer, a salvage specialist, a security guard or even just a chef, Space Station 14 has it all. But be aware, enemy forces are often just minutes away from causing chaos.
